data.description: SELLER TO GIVE BUYER CONCESSIONS TOWARD CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFERS! Take a peek at this adorable home located in the heart of Josephine! Offering 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Kitchen and living is spacious and open. Kitchen provides a generous amount of cabinet and counter space and opens up to the dining area. Living room is cozy and provides great amount of natural light. Primary bedroom has ensuite with shower and tub combo. No carpet. Deck in backyard is great size, perfect for entertaining! Great size yard. NO MUD TAX AND NO HOA!
